parameters:
\N<Boku>Um... it's not good to enter someone's house without
permission, right?

\N<Onee-chan>Oh, Boku-kun. What's wrong? Did you come to
play?

\N<Boku>Um, Onee-chan, there's something I wanted to ask
you...

\N<Onee-chan>Oh, really? Well then, shall we talk inside?
Come on in.
\N<Boku>It's probably better not to bother you so late...
\N<Boku>Huh? The door is locked... Maybe she's out...?
\N<Boku>Ugh... I wonder if it's still not here...
\N<Nana-chan>Hey! Where do you think you're going!
\N<Nana-chan>Hey! Where do you think you're going!
